plain_text.description:
Format:
For UPI id validation,
command|{upi id}

For saving, retrieving cards,
command|{user id}

value.description:
When option_type is color, value will contain an array of objects like:
```json
[
    {
    "name": "first_color",
    "hexcode": "#000000"
    },
    {
    "name": "second_color",
    "hexcode": "#FFFFFF"
    }
]
```
